50" width="110" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Mosque02.svg/220px-Mosque02.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e7/Mosque02.svg/165px-Mosque02.svg.png 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline></td></tr><tr><td class="hlist" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em">
