CCA">'</span>"</a>. This Day. 16 November 2010. Archived from <a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://www.thisdaylive.com/articles/-no-settlement-with-iran-yet-/74044/" id="mwCCE">the original</a> on 2013-05-28.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=%27No+Settlement+with+Iran+Yet%27&amp;rft.date=2010-11-16&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Farticles%2F-no-settlement-with-iran-yet-%2F74044%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AShia+Islam" class="Z3988" about="#mwt582" id="mwCCI"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt582" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}' id="mwCCM"/></span></li><li about="#cite_note-146" id="cite_note-146"><a href="./Shia_Islam#cite_ref-146" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-146" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation web" about="#mwt622" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite web","href":"./Template:Cite_web"},"params":{"url":{"wt":"http://bn.abna24.com/service/important/archive/2011/11/01/275702/story.html"},"title":{"wt":"Shia Population in Bangladesh"},"last":{"wt":""},"first":{"wt":""},"date":{"wt":"November 2011"},"website":{"wt":"World Shia Muslims Population"},"access-date":{"wt":"2018-06-11"},"df":{"wt":"dmy-all"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCCQ"><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="http://bn.abna24.com/service/important/archive/2011/11/01/275702/story.html" id="mwCCU">"Shia Population in Bangladesh"</a>. <i id="mwCCY">World Shia Muslims Population</i>. November 2011<span class="reference-accessdate" id="mwCCc">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap" id="mwCCg">11 June</span> 2018</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val